values:
I witnessed something majorly scary yesterday. Marco-sensei was yelling at someone (I forgot his name...) at the hall, and then he got a little too mad and his glasses shattered. o.o; Seriously, he was like, 'WHAT?' and then bam, those glasses exploded into a million shards. I'm actually worried if he didn't go blind because of those shards. o.o;

I just realized that we actually have homework for Earth Science from oniichan... hope I won't have to do it. I mean, I did come late... So let's just tell Faust-sensei that I never knew.:o

P.E is getting really boring... I mean, we have no balls, or anything else used for sports. (They all miraculously disappeared from the toolshed. o.o;) I heard a bit of music coming from the music room. I'm beginning to wish that I took music instead of P.E... although Hao is sometimes really amusing to watch.
